me.tobiadeyinka.jenkinsci.plugins.builddashboard.job

Class MonitoredJob

  • me.tobiadeyinka.jenkinsci.plugins.builddashboard.job.MonitoredJob

  • public class MonitoredJob

    Defines a job monitored on the dashboard. JsonAutoDetect annotation is set to any to expose the private fields in the responses to data requests from the vue webapp.

    The attributes with types from the jenkins lib are json ignored because they have lots of info that causes a stack overflow during jackson serialization. This is also why the class doesn't just extend the Job class.

      • MonitoredJob

        public MonitoredJob(hudson.model.Job<?,?> job)

        Defines a job monitored on the dashboard. JsonAutoDetect annotation is set to any to expose the private fields in the responses to data requests from the vue webapp.

        The attributes with types from the jenkins lib are json ignored because they have lots of info that causes a stack overflow during jackson serialization. This is also why the class doesn't just extend the Job class.

        Parameters:
        job - The jenkins job represented on the monitor
